  <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>Sleeps 28-32</strong></p>
<p>The Markus is conveniently located in the ever popular Nasserein area, just 5 minutes’ walk from the main gondola for easy skiing access, and with a ski-bus stop just outside the chalet if you’d prefer to ride.</p>
<p>This attractive and stylish chalet combines traditional Tyrolean comfort in the fire-side lounge and attractive dining-room, with well appointed bedrooms and bathrooms throughout, and the added benefit of small extra lounge areas on each floor, should you want to find a quiet corner in which to relax.</p>]]></description>
